  "body": "<center>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1190463977629700178/ec_blue_skies_plugin.png?ex=65a1e4fa&is=658f6ffa&hm=06d243e947bcf4506e83abe757d87a5614404a600d4c64b4e378e59a4715eae9&\" alt=\"EC Mod Plugin for Twilight Forest\" width=\"600\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ec-blue-skies-compat\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_64h.png\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.1.2/assets/cozy/requires/cloth-config-api_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Cloth Config API\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/curios\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1152401406247047188/curios_api_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Cloth Config API\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/expanded-combat\" >\n         <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1152636014880366763/expanded_combat_64h.png\" alt=\"Requires Expanded Combat\" width=\"288\"/>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blue-skies\" >\n         <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/844397409698185227/1190462548697436362/blue_skies_64h.png?ex=65a1e3a5&is=658f6ea5&hm=d9b5299b94ce61c212d9cbab09cebad3626c5c450646dfb46721c24ffe10526e&\" alt=\"Requires Blue Skies\" >\n    </a>\n</p>\n</center>\n\n\n\nA plugin Mod for [Expanded Combat](https://modrinth.com/mod/expanded-combat) adding compatibility with [Blue Skies](https://modrinth.com/mod/blue-skies).\n\n### adds support for:\nBluebright Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nStarlit Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nFrostbright Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nLunar Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nDusk Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nMaple Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nComet Plank - shields, and weapons \\\nLunar Stone - weapons \\\nTurquoise Stone - weapons \\\nCrystallized Plank - weapons \\\nPyrope - shields, weapons, and gauntlets \\\nAquite - shields, weapons, and gauntlets \\\nHorizonite - shields, weapons, and gauntlets \\\nDiopside - shields, weapons, and gauntlets \\\nCharoite - shields, weapons, and gauntlets \\\nFox Pelt - shields \\\nMoonstone - shields \\\nSpike - shields\n\n\\\n\\\nClick the banner to get the discount:\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/userofbricks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/1c1e14ee-b2b9-4507-9143-651ea30d1c04.webp\" alt=\"Bisect Hosting Promotional\">\n    </a>",
